Class HSSFObjectData

java.lang.Object
  org.apache.poi.hssf.usermodel.HSSFObjectData

public final class HSSFObjectData
extends java.lang.Object

Represents binary object (i.e. OLE) data stored in the file. Eg. A GIF, JPEG etc...

Author:
Daniel Noll
